  Bump to latest.

*pulseaudio-2.1-r3 (31 Jul 2013)

  31 Jul 2013; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pulseaudio-2.1-r3.ebuild, -pulseaudio-2.1-r2.ebuild,
  +files/pulseaudio-2.1-clip-setgid.patch:
  Run pulseaudio setgid audio so we can control access to 
  the alsa devices.
  Requires a specific patch to :
   - not try to re-exec() itself as long as LD_BIND_NOW is
   undefined (won't be passed by CLIP's glibc for a setgid
   exe -> loops infinitely)
   - not setresgid(setgid()) which would kind of defeat
   the purpose :)

*pulseaudio-2.1-r2 (27 Dec 2012)

  27 Dec 2012; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
